APPLEACCOUNTTRANSPARENCYD(8)                           System Manager's Manual

NAME
     appleaccounttransparencyd – Apple Account daemon

SYNOPSIS
     appleaccounttransparencyd

DESCRIPTION
     The appleaccounttransparencyd daemon provides Apple Account services and
     serves XPC clients via the com.apple.appleaccount.transparency Mach
     service.

     appleaccounttransparencyd is launched on-demand by launchd(8).  It must
     not be invoked directly by users or processes; all interaction must occur
     through the designated XPC service name.

SEE ALSO
     appleaccountd(8), launchd(8), launchd.plist(5)

